Dia. 01 Suitable?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 expands the living space.
\par If Black plays the placement at 2, White 3 is a suitable move.
\par
\par A and B are miai, so White can easily live. However this variation is not correct.
\par }
