Dia. 02 False eye
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black shouldn't play the placement, but the hane at 1. It is the \cf1\b proper attack\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par Against White 2, Black's placement at 3 is the right order of moves.
\par
\par After White 4, if Black connects at 5, A becomes \cf1\b false eye \cf0\b0 and White dies.
\par
\par
\par }
