Dia. 03 Direction of the Tiger's Mouth Move
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black has to play inside if expanding the living space doesn't work.
\par
\par White's tiger's mouth move at 1 is a powerful vital point. The question is which is the good side to play tiger's mouth move?
\par
\par Black's \cf1\b cut \cf0\b0 at 2 is a\cf1\b  scary move\cf0\b0 .
\par Black 4 becomes sente and White can't live after Black 6.
\par
\par
\par
\par }
